
==>  project currently deployed on https://fj-cms.herokuapp.com/ 


#####################################################################################################
##############################  steps to run the project on localhost  ##############################
#####################################################################################################

1- create python virtual enviorment using this command (before, make sure you already have installed python).

    virtualenv virtualenvName

2- activate the python Enviroment using this command
    
    source virtualenv_name/bin/activate   
    
    for more information follow the link for python enviroment https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/python-virtual-environment/

3- after activating virtualenv, go to the main project folder with manage.py file, and run the following command

    pip install -r requirements.txt 

4- and than run the following command

    python manage.py runserver

5- IF ERROR if statficles do not load properly, run the following command

    python manage.py collectstatic

6- Again run 
    python manage.py runserver


Thanks for reading user guide :) 
